{"tid":1026959,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事]有個耶教傳道既上左黎我屋企門口","createTime":"2019-02-18T12:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T14:10:32.000Z","uid":8386,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9961dcbd2091f016e0ff6ffe3ecd5eaec67f533c","tid":1026959,"uid":8386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"話說我屋企全家都信佛, <br />\n岩岩果個禮拜六有個耶教既中年女教徙,<br />\n就走左上黎我屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我媽, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傳教女人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 你好呀, 我係xx 堂既基督教教友, 我地想搵塵剎, 想派我地今年既刊物俾佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咦？ 我地全家都信佛架喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 唔緊要啦, 你拎去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> . 上帝會指引你地.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 佢依家結左婚搬左出去住啦(佢真係接走左本刊物). 但既然你都上左黎, 總算係一場緣份, 我地都可以結個佛緣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 你等我一陣.<br />\n<br />\n然後我媽入番屋, 行去個香檀前面, 打開左個櫃拎左部迷你版心經出黎.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 你都拎去睇下啦, 可能睇完對你都有幫助架.<br />\n之後對方都收左, 然後我呀媽同佢傾左一陣偈個女耶徙就走左.<br />\n<br />\n我頭先打番屋企同我姨媽傾計, 佢同番我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑左我好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbae0f6a86136aaceb14fe13d7aedfc8ba3fc531","tid":1026959,"uid":54597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"高手"},{"pid":"9db4c696c03abdf82718a718e1a35d88e5098fad","tid":1026959,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTim